{"tid":1630460,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位手足唔好亂咁將阿拉個名塗係地下或者其他地方","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:35:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:05:52.000Z","uid":70545,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15e3dbee4346e72e504803fc0ebf4b897bc6151e","tid":1630460,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n8VXSGa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn8VXSGa.png&h=d7b56800&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sODnjmd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsODnjmd.png&h=2a5f037c&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁樣會令好多支持你地嘅南亞手足變成唔支持你地</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca392c57f4ffe930f3c1369cbbd3ca1e7db1c2d","tid":1630460,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"e9164dbe2c10942de85669e6be061da6f8c6fb2b","tid":1630460,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:42:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"737cb70245cccde96799876547ca4ff9e3311a46","tid":1630460,"uid":44856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8882bfda5a9a03921c96b3ba073c382fa2846dd7","tid":1630460,"uid":208118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"點解噴呢d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc3123cc0b5d2f56b0ba49a6d702518c27b62c4","tid":1630460,"uid":70545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8882bfda5a9a03921c96b3ba073c382fa2846dd7","tid":1630460,"uid":208118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"點解噴呢d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"唔知 不過真係要小心啲"},{"pid":"d74fd50bfbcfbafb75fb63b38627490f51a1fa3b","tid":1630460,"uid":189583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c90460a852f5bb7a57286034e6d2a46eda32c1b3","tid":1630460,"uid":189583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:51:57.000Z","msg":"呢個真係唔好亂噴<br />\n啱啱有巴基斯坦朋友表示覺得好唔尊重"},{"pid":"f5ac9c92d26c1f7cb8341cd6ac7fc3e1b01a597e","tid":1630460,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:56:36.000Z","msg":"個人覺得亂噴無聊咗啲"},{"pid":"8dfb3e0e0b146ccaef86ce94452aead2c9ef73bf","tid":1630460,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:41:05.000Z","ms